{"tid":1490612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！！明天截止！【九龍公園地下空間發展】罔顧樹木生死 創造地下商機？","createTime":"2019-08-20T07:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T09:03:49.000Z","uid":116734,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"408dec2f29f669618cc7d8aab162e74aa69aa9f0","tid":1490612,"uid":116734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:09:46.000Z","msg":"急！！！【明天截止！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KZTf1xN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKZTf1xN.jpg&h=1fab4c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍公園地下空間發展公眾參與】<br />\n🌳🌳🌳立即提交你的意見！<br />\n香港觀鳥會提供的網上請願信：<br />\n<a href=\"https://protectkowloonpark.weebly.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fprotectkowloonpark.weebly.com%2F&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=4d4179f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://protectkowloonpark.weebly.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n【九龍公園地下空間發展】罔顧樹木生死 創造地下商機？<br />\n<br />\n九龍公園是市區的綠肺，也是野生動物在城市中的居所，更是一個著名的城市觀鳥熱點。但來到「第二階段公眾參與」，九龍公園在四個策略性城市地區中被選為優先發展的地下空間。政府建議在九龍公園建造一個以購物商場和停車場為主的地下空間，需要進行大規模的挖掘，摧毀樹木的生存和健康，干擾鳥類的棲息和覓食。我們反對政府以商機取代九龍公園的生態及社會價值，因此反對九龍公園的地下空間發展方案。<br />\n<br />\n在此鼓勵大家了解該計劃的詳情，以及主動表達您的訴求！<br />\n<br />\n***提交意見截止日期：2019年8月21日***<br />\n意見可電郵至：info_urbanunderground@aecom.com<br />\n<br />\n參考資料：<br />\n✍️香港觀鳥會的意見書：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2zedjoN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zedjoN&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c61103bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2zedjoN</a><br />\n👉第二階段公眾參與網站：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2OXLdbZ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OXLdbZ&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=fb224e3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2OXLdbZ</a><br />\n🐦支持鳥類保育工作：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IbTkuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IbTkuK&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=41cba03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IbTkuK</a><br />\n<br />\n【Underground Space Development at Kowloon Park】Implant concrete in green lung for money?<br />\n<br />\nKowloon Park is a green lung in the urban area and an urban refuge for wildlife. It is also a popular birding place. However, when it comes to the &quot;Stage 2 Public Engagement&quot;, Kowloon Park was selected among the four strategic urban areas to develop its underground space with priority. The government proposed an underground space with mainly underground shopping mall and carpark, which requires an extensive surface excavation. This damages the health and survival of the trees and eventually disturbs the roosting and foraging grounds for birds. We consider that it is unacceptable to diminish the ecological, social and amenity value of Kowloon Park for generating commercial value, and thus object to the proposed underground development at Kowloon Park.<br />\n<br />\nLet&rsquo;s take a look at the development proposal and take action to express your view!<br />\n<br />\n***Deadline for submission: 21 August 2019 (Wed)***<br />\nComments can be submitted to: info_urbanunderground@aecom.com<br />\n<br />\nReference: <br />\n✍️HKBWS&rsquo;s submission: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Z6FcgW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Z6FcgW&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=7b93f539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Z6FcgW</a><br />\n👉Official Website for Stage 2 Public Engagement: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33zH6G9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33zH6G9&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=c8ef393c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33zH6G9</a><br />\n🐦Support our Bird Conservation works: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IbTkuK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IbTkuK&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VudLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=41cba03b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IbTkuK</a>"},{"pid":"3f945b9f0541a02b82ff0a2610081b16e2a8baed","tid":1490612,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"Push push push"},{"pid":"94c6571f3fcbfb09c2f146ccaa18a62ab1b7c36e","tid":1490612,"uid":104957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fcbda6e69b6bea656893e366b06fbee6204238d9","tid":1490612,"uid":269409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2e86a47f5957fe1df16b06eae9dcfd1c02e4e708","tid":1490612,"uid":269409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:12:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e48b7c309a3a61a020a9d190c8e8e7106f3d07a1","tid":1490612,"uid":269409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:13:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"589f0de62c64b18a9f752a218beb7d6d42a09afa","tid":1490612,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔反對. 適當既發展對社會係好事"},{"pid":"68802a5dd00c60c622925ed063f1b09c01517fd3","tid":1490612,"uid":172360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"589f0de62c64b18a9f752a218beb7d6d42a09afa","tid":1490612,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔反對. 適當既發展對社會係好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:18:30.000Z","msg":"香港仲發展唔夠？ <br />\n每日150收皮就係好事 唔好再用發展嚟做藉口破壞香港"},{"pid":"0077f0795109c5d8156ab2ee8fd8c2bdc4bf651e","tid":1490612,"uid":69334,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"589f0de62c64b18a9f752a218beb7d6d42a09afa","tid":1490612,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:13:37.000Z","msg":"唔反對. 適當既發展對社會係好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T07:20:26.000Z","msg":"唔反對你老母比狗屌"},{"pid":"529c58ea2fc30a472a7da8dace2d16499649db0e","tid":1490612,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0